<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 14:08:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>本-格维尔在推特上发推文称哈马斯“喜欢”拜登，总统考虑因拉法问题停止美国向以色列运送武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-tweets-hamas-biden-as-president-mulls-halting-u-s-arms-shipments-to-israel/0000018f-5d25-d9a0-a38f-fd27f61e0000</link><description>以色列反对派领导人亚伊尔·拉皮德表示，本·格维尔的推文危及了“每一位以色列国防军士兵和每一位以色列公民”，而财政部长贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇则表示，“尽管有拜登的反对，我们仍将在这场战争中取得彻底胜利”</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 13:32:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-tweets-hamas-biden-as-president-mulls-halting-u-s-arms-shipments-to-israel/0000018f-5d25-d9a0-a38f-fd27f61e0000</guid></item><item><title>当以色列人发现我来自爱尔兰时，他们会问：“你为什么恨我们？”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/when-israelis-find-out-im-from-ireland-they-ask-why-do-you-hate-us/0000018f-5cf6-d0ec-a9cf-deff36c10000</link><description>作为一名出生于爱尔兰、居住在特拉维夫的以色列记者，我被迫应对爱尔兰和以色列之间因加沙战争而不断恶化且经常公开敌对的关系。但我在都柏林的朋友和家人提出的一个问题我很难回答</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 13:23:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/when-israelis-find-out-im-from-ireland-they-ask-why-do-you-hate-us/0000018f-5cf6-d0ec-a9cf-deff36c10000</guid></item><item><title>国家保险研究所数据显示，自 1851 年以来，已有 5000 多名以色列平民在恐怖袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/over-5-000-israeli-civilians-murdered-in-terror-attacks-since-1851-national-data-shows/0000018f-5d47-d0ec-a9cf-df5f2ce60000</link><description>10月7日，以色列与哈马斯战争爆发，共有822名以色列平民被杀害，造成630名儿童成为孤儿，177人成为寡妇，693名父母失去亲人。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 13:19:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/over-5-000-israeli-civilians-murdered-in-terror-attacks-since-1851-national-data-shows/0000018f-5d47-d0ec-a9cf-df5f2ce60000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争期间以色列关系的场景</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/scenes-from-an-israeli-relationship-during-a-war-in-gaza/0000018f-572c-d209-a79f-572d4fdb0000</link><description>当罗特姆·科迪什的伴侣从加沙服役回来后，她发现自己无法像以前一样与他交谈，所以她开始画插图来描述他们所经历的事情。这个每日系列记录了他们最私密的问题，强调了夫妻在战争时期如何应对</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 12:19:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/scenes-from-an-israeli-relationship-during-a-war-in-gaza/0000018f-572c-d209-a79f-572d4fdb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列，孤立吗？不要相信你读到的一切</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-isolated-dont-believe-everything-you-read/0000018f-5d32-d9a0-a38f-fd371d080000</link><description>土耳其与以色列断绝贸易关系是新闻，但其他 120 个国家没有断绝贸易关系并不是新闻。铁的事实仍有待浮出水面，但以色列不应自满</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 12:00:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-isolated-dont-believe-everything-you-read/0000018f-5d32-d9a0-a38f-fd371d080000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡无视每一个警告。现在拜登告诉以色列：“够了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ignored-every-warning-now-biden-is-telling-israel-enough-is-enough/0000018f-5cc6-d0ec-a9cf-dedf3a680000</link><description>由于大约 3,500 枚炸弹的运输目前已停止，美国总统乔·拜登向总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡发出关于在加沙开展地面行动的明确信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 11:36:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ignored-every-warning-now-biden-is-telling-israel-enough-is-enough/0000018f-5cc6-d0ec-a9cf-dedf3a680000</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，独立日前夕以色列人口达到 990 万</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-population-reaches-9-9-million-on-eve-of-independence-day-data-reveals/0000018f-5cd7-d9a0-a38f-fcf7eb620000</link><description>据以色列中央统计局称，到明年独立日，以色列及其约旦河西岸定居点人口预计将超过1000万</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 10:51:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-population-reaches-9-9-million-on-eve-of-independence-day-data-reveals/0000018f-5cd7-d9a0-a38f-fcf7eb620000</guid></item><item><title>以色列摩萨德首次承认：10月7日我们感到惊讶</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-mossad-admits-for-the-first-time-we-were-surprised-on-october-7/0000018f-573f-d6a5-a5ff-d73f93e20000</link><description>尽管与其他组织相比，该情报机构对 10 月 7 日灾难性失败的责任微不足道，但它以多种方式参与了以色列在加沙的活动，主要是卡塔尔资金流向哈马斯</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 10:45:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-mossad-admits-for-the-first-time-we-were-surprised-on-october-7/0000018f-573f-d6a5-a5ff-d73f93e20000</guid></item><item><title>蔑视、否认、忽视：以色列对哈马斯和 10 月 7 日事件的毁灭性情报失败的根源</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/disdain-denial-neglect-the-roots-of-israels-intelligence-failure-on-hamas-and-oct-7/0000018f-5811-d348-a7bf-feb907a80000</link><description>2021 年加沙战争结束后，以色列军事情报部门就加沙哈马斯的真正威胁做出了一系列重大决定。从压制不同意见到淘汰单位，“失败链”就是这样发生的</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 10:05:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/disdain-denial-neglect-the-roots-of-israels-intelligence-failure-on-hamas-and-oct-7/0000018f-5811-d348-a7bf-feb907a80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列顶级武器制造商无意中透露了其最大的外国客户：印度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-giant-iai-unwittingly-reveals-its-largest-foreign-customer/0000018f-583d-d348-a7bf-febdda230000</link><description>事实证明，去年印度占以色列航空航天工业公司出口收入的四分之一。以色列公司的年度报告中还披露了阿塞拜疆和摩洛哥的详细信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 09:14:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-giant-iai-unwittingly-reveals-its-largest-foreign-customer/0000018f-583d-d348-a7bf-febdda230000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防雇员因严重性犯罪被监禁十多年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-employee-incarcerated-for-over-a-decade-for-severe-sexual-offenses/0000018f-5c54-d1d4-afcf-fc5e323c0000</link><description>这位前国防机构雇员十多年前因滥用职权对其他雇员进行性伤害而被起诉，并被判犯有严重性犯罪罪</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 08:55:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-employee-incarcerated-for-over-a-decade-for-severe-sexual-offenses/0000018f-5c54-d1d4-afcf-fc5e323c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军命名以色列士兵在黎巴嫩边境附近被迫击炮弹炸死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/idf-names-israeli-soldier-killed-by-mortar-shell-near-lebanon-border/0000018f-5c3f-d65e-a9cf-dfbf6b370000</link><description>20 岁的上士海姆·萨巴赫 (Haim Sabach) 最初在军队担任后端职务，后来要求调到其他职位。他因在加沙战争期间的服役而获得了卓越证书</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 07:52:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/idf-names-israeli-soldier-killed-by-mortar-shell-near-lebanon-border/0000018f-5c3f-d65e-a9cf-dfbf6b370000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，内塔尼亚胡因最近的健康问题而被伪装的救护车跟踪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-reportedly-followed-by-disguised-ambulance-following-recent-health-issues/0000018f-5c2a-d0ec-a9cf-de3f2a960000</link><description>虽然在以色列前总理办公室工作的消息人士表示，救护车只是在特殊情况下总理车队的一部分，但消息人士告诉以色列新闻媒体瓦拉，即使在主要医院附近行驶时，内塔尼亚胡的救护车也会在场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 07:37:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-reportedly-followed-by-disguised-ambulance-following-recent-health-issues/0000018f-5c2a-d0ec-a9cf-de3f2a960000</guid></item><item><title>美国决定推迟向以色列运送武器可能会影响以色列国防军在其他方面的准备情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/u-s-decision-to-delay-arms-shipments-could-impact-idfs-readiness-on-other-fronts/0000018f-5ad4-d9a0-a38f-fef7551e0000</link><description>国防官员已警告政治领导人危机的严重性，并敦促他们尽快与华盛顿达成谅解</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 03:00:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/u-s-decision-to-delay-arms-shipments-could-impact-idfs-readiness-on-other-fronts/0000018f-5ad4-d9a0-a38f-fef7551e0000</guid></item><item><title>控制拉法口岸意味着以色列再次占领加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/taking-control-of-the-rafah-crossing-means-that-israel-is-once-against-occupying-gaza/0000018f-5ae3-d9a0-a38f-fee787130000</link><description>从以色列的角度来看，此举具有军事合理性，根据国际法可能会产生影响，并可能使耶路撒冷与开罗的关系复杂化</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 03:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/taking-control-of-the-rafah-crossing-means-that-israel-is-once-against-occupying-gaza/0000018f-5ae3-d9a0-a38f-fee787130000</guid></item><item><title>前往加沙的援助卡车车队被抗议者封锁；以色列北部警报响起</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article-live/biden-u-s-will-halt-arms-shipments-to-israel-if-it-goes-ahead-with-rafah-invasion/0000018f-5b18-d65e-a9cf-dfb8da4c0000</link><description>世界卫生组织：拉法医院的燃料将在三天内耗尽 ■ 以色列总统称极右翼部长针对拜登的言论“损害了以色列的国家安全利益” ■ 黎巴嫩报道：四名真主党成员在以色列北部袭击中丧生 ■ 叙利亚：以色列导弹前往大马士革地区被击落</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 02:13:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article-live/biden-u-s-will-halt-arms-shipments-to-israel-if-it-goes-ahead-with-rafah-invasion/0000018f-5b18-d65e-a9cf-dfb8da4c0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登：如果拉法继续入侵美国将停止向以色列运送武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/biden-u-s-will-halt-arms-shipments-to-israel-if-it-continues-with-rafah-invasion/0000018f-5a44-d9a0-a38f-fe67a68a0000</link><description>美国总统在接受美国有线电视新闻网采访时表示，他告诉总理内塔尼亚胡，如果以色列进入加沙人口中心，将不会得到美国的支持</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 22:19:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/biden-u-s-will-halt-arms-shipments-to-israel-if-it-continues-with-rafah-invasion/0000018f-5a44-d9a0-a38f-fe67a68a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军前主席：以色列必须停止加沙战争以确保人质获释</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/former-idf-chief-israel-must-halt-gaza-war-to-secure-release-of-hostages/0000018f-5a15-d65e-a9cf-dfb57e5c0000</link><description>在周三播出的采访中，阿维夫·科查维还承认，以色列在 10 月 7 日之前未能认识到哈马斯是一个生存威胁</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 21:42:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/former-idf-chief-israel-must-halt-gaza-war-to-secure-release-of-hostages/0000018f-5a15-d65e-a9cf-dfb57e5c0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔批准晋升因对抗议者施暴而接受调查的以色列警官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-approves-promotion-of-police-officer-under-probe-for-violence-against-protesters/0000018f-59ce-d348-a7bf-ffef6bc10000</link><description>梅厄·苏伊萨（Meir Suissa）目前因多起暴力事件（包括对以色列抗议者使用眩晕手榴弹）而受到以色列警察内部调查部门的调查，他已被晋升为特拉维夫南部地区负责人，立即生效</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 20:29:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-approves-promotion-of-police-officer-under-probe-for-violence-against-protesters/0000018f-59ce-d348-a7bf-ffef6bc10000</guid></item><item><title>官方律师称，内塔尼亚胡在欺诈案中没有询问礼物的合法性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-didnt-ask-about-legality-of-gifts-in-fraud-case-official-counsel-says/0000018f-59c2-d0ec-a9cf-dfdfc5a70000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的辩护律师称他的法律顾问“有偏见”，因为内塔尼亚胡作证称总理直到 2018 年才就“朋友的礼物”问题与她接触，因此法官选择不干预。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 20:20:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-didnt-ask-about-legality-of-gifts-in-fraud-case-official-counsel-says/0000018f-59c2-d0ec-a9cf-dfdfc5a70000</guid></item></channel></rss>